<span  style="font-family: Plus Jakarta Sans;">Outposts are present in Level 96, though they are temporary. Such settlements are in the form of small survey teams, resource extraction points, mapping stations, or transit checkpoints rather than permanent settlements. Nevertheless, encountering them can be common, as the level is a common interest for research groups.</span>

<span  style="font-family: Plus Jakarta Sans;">Below is a list of groups whose presence and their official reasons are documented or declassified:</span>

<div  style="font-family: Plus Jakarta Sans;">
=== <span style="font-family: Explore; font-size: 22px;">[[M.E.G.|Major Explorer Group]] (MEG)</span> ===
